data.clean_description: LSD Lysergic acid diethylamide is known by street names such as as acid , blotter , lucy , smilies , paper mushrooms , stars , tabs , M , window panes , sunshine or trips. It is a semi-synthetic psychedelic drug which originates from ergot , a type of grain fungus that typically grows on rye and is the most widely known of the hallucinogenic drugs. It is an extremely potent and an illegal Class A drug.
